text: Edward Webster (ante 1691 - 1755) was Member of the Parliament of Ireland for Carysfort from 1717 to 1727Search Ulster Historical Foundation - Biographies of Members of the Irish Parliament 1692-1800 and Chief Secretary to The Duke of Bolton as Lord Lieutenant of Ireland from 1717 to 1720. ==References== Category:1755 deaths Category:Chief Secretaries for Ireland Category:Irish MPs 1715–1727 Category:Members of the Privy Council of Ireland Category:Members of the Parliament of Ireland (pre-1801) for County Wicklow constituencies Category:1691 births
